{"tid":1777699,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"柒婆眼中的自由 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-12-10T11:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T11:55:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1fb39bc8e18c0c5df35f2988ec68c8dc43d9c3","tid":1777699,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191210/20822004/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191210%2F20822004%2F&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cf4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=ddb37fd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191210%2F20822004%2F&h=9dadcc69\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191210/20822004/</a><br />\n<br />\n柒婆眼中的自由 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191210/large/1575875089_1085.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575875089_1085.jpg&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cf4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=2ab0dfc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191210/large/1575875089_1085.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191210/large/1575875089_1085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575875089_1085.jpg&h=ddf3d842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12月8號，國際人權日，80萬（許多遊行者認為超過120萬）香港人由維園遊行至中環遮打道，用行動告訴香港政府，不正面回應五大訴求，香港人永遠不會放棄。<br />\n<br />\n不知道香港人哪一方面自由受損的柒婆，大約可以厚着臉皮說，香港人仍擁有遊行自由。事實是，遊行雖然收到警方不反對通知書，但未起步已收到黑旗警告。遊行隊伍沿途更不斷受到警方挑釁。香港人還擁有免於恐懼的自由嗎？<br />\n<br />\n關於自由，柒婆的理解有異於常人，幾個月前，柒婆閉門會議錄音流出，她抱怨自己失去自由，「我沒有去過商場，又不能去髮廊。」她治下的香港由國際金融中心變成第三世界，風雨飄搖，民眾活在恐懼之下，她抱怨的是失去去髮廊的自由。香港人對她的髮型不感興趣，反而想知道她為甚麼還不辭職，她究竟有沒有辭職的自由？有沒有想做甚麼的自由？有沒有不做甚麼的自由？<br />\n<br />\n坐特區第三把交椅的鄭若驊，在倫敦仆街之後，本來宣布花一年半載時間養傷，神隱英國。卻突然回到香港，而且是由北京飛回香港，昔日神采不見，一派灰頭土臉。外媒透露她被送中。不知道柒婆知不知道鄭若驊除了擁有着樽領衫的自由之外，是否擁有行動自由？是否擁有心靈自由？是否擁有自由意志？是否擁有免於恐懼的自由？是否擁有劈炮唔撈的自由？<br />\n<br />\n不知道香港人哪一方面的自由受損的柒婆，有沒有說出真相的自由？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"bd8436070bfef45d154dfda93ac635911792b72d","tid":1777699,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細議會仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入 －－》 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cf4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=c663adf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"762fd4f09b2153f32174fc7d090497399ebc2371","tid":1777699,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"sorry 借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 